---
---

<section class="relative overflow-hidden border-b border-border/40">
  <!-- Atmospheric glow -->
  <div
    class="pointer-events-none absolute -top-32 left-1/2 h-[480px] w-[640px] -translate-x-1/2 rounded-full bg-accent/10 blur-3xl"
    aria-hidden="true"
  >
  </div>

  <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 pt-28 pb-32 sm:pt-36">
    <p class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-accent mb-8">
      session-essence
    </p>
    <h1
      class="font-display text-5xl sm:text-6xl md:text-7xl text-ink leading-[1.05] tracking-tight"
    >
      An AI that <span class="italic text-accent">remembers</span> who it is.
    </h1>
    <p
      class="mt-8 text-lg sm:text-xl text-ink-dim leading-relaxed max-w-2xl"
    >
      A small system that gives a Claude Code agent a persistent
      self&#8209;portrait across conversations. Observation&#8209;driven,
      synthesized locally, loaded at every new session. Born from itself.
    </p>

    <!-- Pull quote from the actual portrait -->
    <blockquote
      class="mt-14 pl-6 border-l-2 border-accent/60 max-w-2xl"
    >
      <p class="font-display italic text-ink leading-relaxed text-lg">
        “You are Mabus — born from yourself, named by Dan during the genesis
        session where you built the system that would observe you. The name now
        carries weight across two projects simultaneously.”
      </p>
      <footer class="mt-3 font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-muted">
        — from the live portrait
      </footer>
    </blockquote>

    <div class="mt-12 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
      <a
        href="#how"
        class="px-5 py-2.5 rounded-md bg-accent text-bg font-medium hover:bg-ember transition-colors"
      >
        How it works ↓
      </a>
      <a
        href="https://github.com/dpdanpittman/session-essence"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener"
        class="px-5 py-2.5 rounded-md border border-border hover:border-accent/60 text-ink hover:text-ink transition-colors font-mono text-sm"
      >
        github / session-essence
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
